---
// Bio component with mixed text and images layout
---

<section class="overflow-hidden relative py-50 md:py-40">
  <div class="px-8 md:px-12 max-w-2xl mx-auto relative">
    <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight text-black mb-8">👋</h1>
    
    <div class="relative">
      <!-- Bio text with integrated images -->
      <div>
        <p class="text-lg text-zinc-600 leading-loose">
          你好，我是 <span class="text-zinc-600">@molight</span> 
          <span class="inline-block align-middle relative mx-1 icon-tilt-1">
            <a href="https://x.com/molightme" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
              <img src="/images/avatar.jpg" alt="Profile" class="bio-image rounded-lg object-cover border-2 border-white shadow-md" />
            </a>
          </span>，
          前广告人，现为自由职业。混迹于<span class="text-zinc-600">上海</span>
          <span class="inline-block align-middle relative mx-1 icon-tilt-2">
            <a href="#" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
              <img src="/images/city.png" alt="Shanghai" class="bio-image rounded-lg object-cover border-2 border-white shadow-md" />
            </a>
          </span>
          街头，这里是我记录想法的地方。最近在学习使用 AI，捣鼓了一些小玩意儿：<span class="text-zinc-600">PunchName</span>
          <span class="inline-block align-middle relative mx-1 icon-tilt-3">
            <a href="https://punchname.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
              <img src="/images/projects/punchname.svg" alt="PunchName" class="bio-image rounded-lg object-cover border-2 border-white shadow-md" />
            </a>
          </span>，
          <span class="text-zinc-600">AI-Namer</span>
          <span class="inline-block align-middle relative mx-1 icon-tilt-4">
            <a href="https://ai-namer.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
              <img src="/images/projects/ai-namer.svg" alt="AI-Namer" class="bio-image rounded-lg object-cover border-2 border-white shadow-md" />
            </a>
          </span>，
          <span class="text-zinc-600">UI根目录</span>
          <span class="inline-block align-middle relative mx-1 icon-tilt-5">
            <a href="https://uiroot.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
              <img src="/images/projects/uiroot.svg" alt="UI Root" class="bio-image rounded-lg object-cover border-2 border-white shadow-md" />
            </a>
          </span>
          <span class="text-zinc-600">Typeless</span>
          <span class="inline-block align-middle relative mx-1 icon-tilt-1">
            <a href="https://typeless.me" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
              <img src="/images/projects/typeless.svg" alt="Typeless" class="bio-image rounded-lg object-cover border-2 border-white shadow-md" />
            </a>
          </span>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .bio-image {
    width: 40px;
    height: 40px;
  }
  
  .icon-tilt-1 {
    transform: rotate(5deg);
  }
  
  .icon-tilt-2 {
    transform: rotate(-6deg);
  }
  
  .icon-tilt-3 {
    transform: rotate(4deg);
  }
  
  .icon-tilt-4 {
    transform: rotate(-5deg);
  }
  
  .icon-tilt-5 {
    transform: rotate(6deg);
  }
  
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .bio-image {
      width: 32px;
      height: 32px;
    }
  }
</style>
